docstring.long_description: This block reads a log file from the CSS Electronics CL2000 logger and returns a list of can.Message. The file is expected to follow the CL2000 documentation: https://canlogger.csselectronics.com/clx000-docs/cl2000/log/index.html#data-fields
docstring.short_description: Read the log file from the CSS Electronics CL2000 logger and return a list of can.Message

returns.description: List with all message with the can.Message format
